Name: Sambassadeur

text: Sambassadeur are a Swedish pop band formed in 2003 in Gothenburg. They are named after the Serge Gainsbourg song "Les Sambassadeurs."[1] The band are signed to the Labrador label, and to date, they have released four studio albums and a handful of EPs and singles. Their third album, European, was released in February 2010.[2]
